Description

Split Test Cell for R&D Coin Cell Battery

The EQ-STC Split Test Cell is used for rechargeable battery and battery electrode materials research. Optional sizes at 10, 12, 15, 19, 20, 24 mm diameter cell.

SPECIFICATIONS

  • Structure :Full stainless steel
  • Max.CellThickness:6mm (cathode+separator+anode)
  • Features:
    1. A6mmheightspacerinsidethetestcelltopressdownonthe elecctrode andpreventtheelectrodefromcurling.
    2. Sealedbyelectrolytecorrosive-proofPTFEO-rings
    3. Electrolytecorrosive-proofPTFEguidesleevecapableofwithstanding temperatures upto250C.
    4. Easytoseparateaftertesting
    5. Smallenoughtobeputinandtakenoutfromaglovebox
    6. Samefunctionalityto“CoinCell”butwithmoresizeoptionsfor electrodeand separator and also the proper dimensions for glove box compatibility
  • Optional :10,12,15,19,20,and24mmdiametercustomized
  • Dimensions :80mm*80mm
